data.description: Welcome to 3308 Avenida Sierra, nestled in the picturesque community of Lomas Serenas. This one level Executive Entertaining Pool Home ahy od HALF ACRE awaits you. A Meticulous 3 Bed, 2.5 Bath Residence offers a serene style of living at 2,551 sq. feet. As you approach, you'll be greeted by the elegance of a paved driveway with rich earth tones that complement the surrounding lovely landscape. As you step inside, the Acacia wood flooring steals the spotlight, infusing every room with natural warmth and timeless elegance. The rich, honey-toned wood adds character and sophistication to the living spaces, complementing the many classy upgrades that adorn this home. This home is designed to captivate you with vaulted ceilings and gleaming light. The heart of this home is the elegantly remodeled kitchen, offering both functionality and style. Granite, Stainless Appliances, Soft Close Cabinetry simply perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Gorgeous Remodeled Bathrooms with Carrara Marble and Granite add sophistication and a touch of luxury to this already exceptional home. Your environmental footprint is lightened by 24 fully PAID SOLAR, newer windows, ensuring energy efficiency and lower utility costs. Step out and you'll discover a true oasis - a larege saltwater pool and spa, ideal for entertaining with family or friends. This breathless of a  backyard is a paradise to lush landscaping, abundance of trees, plants & vibrant flowers. Fruit trees consist of Lemon/Orange/Tangelo/Pineapple Guava, Apricot/Cumquats/Avocado and Hawaiian Ginger. This natural beauty not only enhances the aesthetics of the property but also provides a peaceful and serene backdrop for outdoor living. As a bonus, this property also attracts a variety of unique birds, including many hummingbirds, making it a haven for wildlife enthusiasts. A nature lover's delight. 3 car garage w/new modern doors, custom Pacific Panel Cabinets throughout home, epoxy floors, ample attic storage. All this completes the practical side of this property, ensuring all your belongings are well-organized and accessible. Enjoy a whole-house water conditioner enhances the water quality throughout the home, providing you with pure and refreshing water for daily living.  This home is an invitation to a life of serenity, elegance, and the quintessential California indoor-outdoor lifestyle offering so many features to see. ROOM FOR POSSIBLE ADU!  Must See Supplements.
